1. *Leo* je prelepa mačka. (The lion is a beautiful cat.)
2. Moj stariji brat *leže* sa svojom devojkom na kauču. (My older brother is lying with his girlfriend on the couch.)
3. Kada je sunce izašlo, *lepa* šuma je bila puna života. (When the sun came out, the beautiful forest was full of life.)
4. Ona je kupila crveni *leptir* za svoju sobu. (She bought a red butterfly for her room.)
5. On je polagao svoj *lezaj* u sobi. (He was laying his bed in the room.)